---
title: Turkish-Spiced Chicken in Apricot Sauce with Lemon Almond Rice & Harissa-Roasted Carrots
description: Sure, you could have plain chicken for dinner—but why not dig into this warmly-spiced version that’s smothered in tangy apricot pan sauce instead? Here, we season the chicken with a Turkish spice blend of cumin, garlic, coriander, allspice, and chili flakes, then serve it with a jammy, buttery apricot sauce and pair it all with spicy harissa-roasted carrots and almond-studded rice. You’d be chicken not to try it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6138d8d05acb2c613858e349-be339f82.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/turkish-spiced-chicken-in-apricot-sauce-6138d8d05acb2c613858e349-7d07c77f.pdf
